race.description: Book A Christmas Party @ Crjc Handicap (Bm66)
race.comment: STEEL IMPACT (10) has switched from Ciaron Maher to little brother Declan since a respectable fifth over the mile at Eagle Farm. Placed three in a row prior to that over today's trip in Victoria. Has the right form to stretch this field. TESER (2) had his first run for the Brett Bellamy stable recently and was an eye-catcher in a Class 3 over 1400m at the Gold Coast. Nicely placed over the extra trip and although it's been a while between drinks he is a definite contender. MONTGOMERY (5) mixes his form and is more at home on a track with give. Worth including if a soft 5 is posted. WARRIOR HEAD (6) has been racing well in Queensland and from a good draw can play a big role in the finish. GAVIN (4) is a model of consistency and should enjoy a nice run up on the speed.
